presentationColumns.name: Item Product Line Family
presentationColumns.description:
Based On Segment 5 (Product Line) from the Sales Account defined in the Item attributes:

CASE  "SSYS"."Dim - Item"."Item Product Line Segment Code"   
   WHEN '890' then   'Service'
   WHEN '999' then   'FDM-Service'
   WHEN '400' then   'MB - Systems'
   WHEN '410' then   'MB - Systems'
   WHEN '430' then   'MB - SP'
   WHEN '470' then   'MB - Consumables'  
ELSE
   CASE WHEN CAST("SSYS"."Dim - Item"."Item Product Line Segment Code" AS DOUBLE)  BETWEEN 101 and 189 THEN 'Equipment'
             WHEN CAST("SSYS"."Dim - Item"."Item Product Line Segment Code" AS DOUBLE)    BETWEEN 191 AND 199 THEN 'SUBCONTRACTOR'  
            WHEN CAST("SSYS"."Dim - Item"."Item Product Line Segment Code" AS DOUBLE)  BETWEEN 281 and 299 THEN 'FDM-Equipment Other'  
            WHEN CAST("SSYS"."Dim - Item"."Item Product Line Segment Code" AS DOUBLE)  BETWEEN 201 and 280 THEN 'FDM-Equipment'  
  
   ELSE  
      CASE  LEFT("SSYS"."Dim - Item"."Item Product Line Segment Code"   , 1)   
         WHEN  '5' THEN 'Resins'
         WHEN  '6' THEN 'Resins'
         WHEN  '7' THEN 'FDM-Consumable'
         WHEN  '8' THEN 'Service'
         WHEN  '9' THEN 'FDM-Service'
      ELSE 
         CASE WHEN "SSYS"."Dim - Item"."User Item Type" = 'FRT'  THEN 'Freight'
                   ELSE 'Other'
         END
      END
   END
END
